articles.title: Bumrah Yorks Yashasvi Jaiswal in Dublin Nets, Brings Out his Epic Celebration: WATCH VIDEO - News18
articles.description: Jasprit Bumrah, who will lead India in the 3 T20Is against Ireland, was seen bowling at full tilt, a comforting sight ahead of the upcoming Asia Cup and the ODI World Cup
articles.content: The Jasprit Bumrah-led Team India has arrived in Ireland and has begun training for the three-match T20I series against the hosts, starting August 18 in Dublin. A bunch of youngsters is getting ready… [+2136 chars]
